Package gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2.index

Interface Summary
Index An index abstraction.
ModelIndexer An entity providing indexing services for an RDF model.
ModelView A ModelView provides priviledged access to the nodes contained in a RDF model.
ObjectViewSupport A helper for supporting "object view" access methods (defined in gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2.views).
TripleDeletionListener A callback interface that is used by Model and ModelIndexer so that the latter can notify the former about triple deletions.
 

Class Summary
EmptyTriplesList An empty List of Triples.
HorizontalModelIndexer A ModelIndexer implementation, used only for testing.
ModelIndexers A class containing static factory methods creating ModelIndexer instances.
TripleBasedObjectViewSupport An default implementation of ObjectViewSupport.
